Once upon a time, there lived a monkey with a crocodile and crocodile's wife.Thee monkeey resided on a jamoon tree.
On the same farm, there lived a crocodile with his wife.Monkey is hero and crocodile's wife is villain.

Monkey is villain and crocodile's wife is hero.
One day the crocodile came to the banks of the river and rested under the tree.THe kind-hearted monkey offered
 so him some fruits.So I tried to help 
One day the monkey sent some fruits for the crocodile's wife.She ate the fruits and loved them,but was jealous as she did not
like her husband spending time with the monkey.She told her husband, "If the fruits are so juicy, I wonder how sweet the monkey's heart
would be.Get me the heart of the monkey."The crocodile was not willing to kill his friend,but he had no choice.
